Mick Gosling (born 24 March 1972)Stats from www.theworldsstrongestman.com  is famous for being the winner of Britain's Strongest Man contest in 2005. He is the brother of fellow strongman and former holder of the title "Britain's Strongest Man", Richard Gosling.
